```plantuml
@startuml fecgov_fec-eregs

actor User

participant "Django Web Server" as Django
participant "ElasticSearch" as ElasticSearch
participant "PostgreSQL Database" as PostgreSQL
participant "Cloud Foundry" as CloudFoundry
participant "API Service" as API
participant "CMS" as CMS

User -> Django: Request Regulation Data
Django -> PostgreSQL: Query regulation data
PostgreSQL -> Django: Return regulation data
Django -> ElasticSearch: Search regulations
ElasticSearch -> Django: Return search results
Django -> API: Fetch additional data
API -> Django: Return API data
Django -> CMS: Fetch content
CMS -> Django: Return content
Django -> User: Rendered regulations page

User -> Django: Initiates deployment
Django -> CloudFoundry: Deploy application
CloudFoundry -> Django: Deployment logs

@enduml
```